    "content": "server/src/image_tool/color.py :: rgb_to_ycbcr\ndef rgb_to_ycbcr(r: int, g: int, b: int) -> tuple[int, int, int]:\n    y = int(0.299 * r + 0.587 * g + 0.114 * b)\n    cb = int(-0.168736 * r - 0.331264 * g + 0.5 * b + 128)\n    cr = int(0.5 * r - 0.418688 * g - 0.081312 * b + 128)\n    return (\n        max(0, min(255, y)),\n        max(0, min(255, cb)),\n        max(0, min(255, cr)),\n    )",
